conditional statement:
to make the set of instruction execute only when the given condition is truw>
used to decide where the code have to be executed or skip
it executes in sequence
Block of code:set of instruction
it will execute only when the specific condition is true
condition:an expression that evaluates an result(true or false)
ex:console.log(5>6)
methodS:
if:oly one possible condition
it the condition is true it will execute ther wise it skip
Syntax:
